<HEADLINE> Flash: Russia Qualifies for Women's Volleyball </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
HONG KONG, September 12 (Xinhua) -- Reigning World Grand Prix
title holder Russia beat host and two-time world champion China
4-15, 15-11, 15-13, 10-15, 15-13 in the semi-finals to qualify for
the final at the GD Guangdong Cup World Women's Volleyball Grand
Prix Finals here on Saturday.
</P>
<P>
In the final Sunday afternoon, Russia will play two-time World
Grand Prix champion Brazil which beat Olympic champion Cuba 15-6,
17-16, 11-15, 17-15 in an earlier semi-final match on Saturday of
the two-day finals here. 
