<HEADLINE> German Federation Chief Might Quit </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
BONN, September 12 (Xinhua) -- German Soccer Federation (DFB)
president Egidius Braun said he was considering retirement here
today.
</P>
<P>
