<HEADLINE> Flash: Brazil Qualifies for Volleyball Grand Prix Finals </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
HONG KONG, September 12 (Xinhua) -- Two-time World Grand Prix
champions Brazil upset world and Olympic champions Cuba 3-1 in
the semi-finals here on Saturday to qualify for the final of the
on-going GD Guangdong Cup World Women's Volleyball Grand Prix F
inals starting at the Hong Kong Coliseum here.
</P>
<P>
Brazil defeated Cuba 15-6, 17-16, 11-15, 17-15 for the final
berth. In the final Sunday afternoon, Brazil will face the
winners of the weekend's other semi-final here, between two-time
world champions China and reigning World Grand Prix title holders
Russia. 
</P>
</TEXT>
