<HEADLINE> Kuwait Stock Exchange Index Surges </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
KUWAIT CITY, September 12 (Xinhua) -- The Kuwait Stock Exchange
index edged up 14.8 points to close at 2,188.9 points Saturday.
</P>
<P>
The trading volume and value all increased as a total of 158.36
million shares changed hands in over 3,355 deals, as against
129.98 million shares over 2,891 deals traded last Wednesday.
</P>
<P>
The value of trading rose to 30.12 million Kuwaiti dinars
(99.39 million U.S. dollars) from last Wednesday's 26.39 million
dinars (89.08 million U.S. dollars). 
</P>
</TEXT>
