<HEADLINE> Gold Price in Hong Kong Down </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
HONG KONG, September 12 (Xinhua) -- The gold price in Hong Kong
fell 10 HK dollars to close at 2,677 HK dollars a tael on
Saturday, according to Po Sang Bank, one of the major gold dealers
in Hong Kong.
</P>
<P>
The gold price is equivalent to 289.98 U.S. dollars a troy
ounce, 1.09 U.S. dollars down from the previous close at
Saturday's exchange rate of one U.S. dollar to 7.7490 HK dollars.
</P>
