<HEADLINE> New Bearing Venture Opens in Dalian </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
DALIAN, September 12 (Xinhua) -- The Dalian THK Co. Ltd, a
Sino-Japanese joint venture, recently opened in this major port
city in northeast China.
</P>
